complete será de R$50,00 por partida.</p><p>• Isso significa que, se um time X precisar de complete em 3 partidas, o custo total será de R$150,00.</p><p>• O pagamento deverá ser realizado antecipadamente, antes do início da partida.</p></div><label class=\"flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group\"><input type=\"checkbox\" required=\"\" class=\"mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-primary/30 bg-dark/50 text-primary focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-0\" name=\"aceitaTermos\"/><span class=\"text-light group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Li e concordo com os termos sobre complete *</span></label></div><div><label class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Comprovante de Pagamento *</label><div class=\"relative\"><input type=\"file\" id=\"comprovante\" required=\"\" accept=\"image/*,.pdf\" class=\"hidden\"/><label for=\"comprovante\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full px-4 py-6 bg-dark/50 border-2 border-dashed border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light hover:border-primary hover:bg-dark/70 transition-all cursor-pointer group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-upload w-6 h-6 text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><polyline points=\"17 8 12 3 7 8\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg><span class=\"font-semibold\">Clique para enviar o comprovante</span></label></div><p class=\"text-light/60 text-sm mt-2\">Formatos aceitos: JPG, PNG, PDF (máx. 5MB)</p></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-primary text-dark font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 disabled:bg-primary/50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\" tabindex=\"0\">Enviar Inscrição</button></form></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gr